{
  "application": "LSF",
  "details": {
    "script_purpose": "Submit an OpenMPI job to the LSF (Load Sharing Facility) cluster",
    "libraries": [
      "mpirun",
      "opagetvf_env",
      "iba_select_mpi",
      "iba_getpsm_func"
    ],
    "environment_variables": [
      "MPICH_PREFIX",
      "mpirunfile",
      "vfselectmethod",
      "vfname",
      "vfsid",
      "dsprtg",
      "qname",
      "mrailmap",
      "MPI_CMD_ARGS",
      "LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
      "LSB_DJOB_NUMPROC",
      "OMPI_MCA_btl_openib_pkey",
      "OMPI_MCA_btl_openib_ib_service_level",
      "OMPI_MCA_btl_openib_mtu",
      "OMPI_MCA_mtl_psm_ib_pkey",
      "OMPI_MCA_mtl_psm_ib_service_level",
      "PSM_MTU",
      "OMPI_MCA_mtl_psm_path_query",
      "OMPI_MCA_mtl_psm_ib_service_id",
      "routing",
      "PSM_PATH_SELECTION",
      "PSM_MULTIRAIL",
      "PSM_MULTIRAIL_MAP"
    ],
    "input_arguments": [
      "-p num_processes",
      "-V vf_select_method",
      "-s vf_sid",
      "-n vf_name",
      "-d dsp_rtg",
      "-q queue_name",
      "-m <unit:port>[,<unit:port>]",
      "mpi_run_file"
    ],
    "job_submission": "bsub"
  }
}
